# CTX runtime cache (elicited.json, telemetry, observed-confidence state).
# Per-task spec docs at .ctx-cache/tasks/ stay tracked — they're the
# paper trail for the CP-NNN discipline (see paper/code-packer-v0-backlog.md).
.ctx-cache/*
!.ctx-cache/tasks/

# Generated binaries (keep .md source, regenerate with paper/md_to_docx.py)
paper/*.docx

# Generated scaling test corpora (regenerate with scaling_runner.py)
ctxpack/benchmarks/scaling/scaling_corpora/

# Working notes and internal files (not part of the project)
rough_notes.md
